{"tid":2288491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"壹傳媒上半年虧損按年收窄54%","createTime":"2020-11-16T13:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T00:11:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e82d2fbdbd33386e899632ecd5186ff52fcc0ea5","tid":2288491,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rRyApB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rRyApB.jpg&h=9b8cfb9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒截至9月底止6個月虧損1.45億元，按年收窄近54%。不派中期息。<br />\n<br />\n集團上半年總收益上升2.4%，接近5.7億元。香港及其他地區經營業務佔總收益升至82%，台灣業務佔總收益降至18%。<br />\n<br />\n期內數碼業務虧損3170萬元，按年減少51.2%，外部收益3.03億元，按年增加34.7%，網上訂閱收入的增長部分被數碼廣告收益的跌幅抵銷。印刷業務總收益2.66億元，按年減少19.6%，虧損約1.03億元，按年收窄58.2%，主要由於有效成本控制。<br />\n<br />\n截至9月底，蘋果日報香港登記會員基數約380萬人，當中63萬人屬付費訂閱。<br />\n<br />\n集團6月至8月獲得香港政府「補就業」計劃資助3300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560322-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560322-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fuylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=6f0e2c7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560322-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=99746616\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560322-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"05599a2f62ea7fb2b4c6df51923796aac0acad77","tid":2288491,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"集團6月至8月獲得香港政府「補就業」計劃資助3300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔計就輸兩億"},{"pid":"021590480a67be51987b5d9ae4bb0731e5e7a758","tid":2288491,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"c